longBusinessSummary: Knaus Tabbert AG, together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and sells leisure vehicles in Europe. It operates through Premium and Luxury segments. The company offers motorhomes, caravans, and camper vans under the KNAUS, TABBERT, WEINSBERG, T@B, and MORELO brands. It also operates RENT AND TRAVEL digital portal for renting leisure vehicles through a network of partners operating approximately 180 rental stations. Knaus Tabbert AG was founded in 1912 and is headquartered in Jandelsbrunn, Germany.
